  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/0a8903dd3a4b9cfd37c396ee753c8568.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/0a8903dd3a4b9cfd37c396ee753c8568.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a new series of intricate boxes filled with alluring enigmas and brain-teasing challenges that will leave you a lasting impression</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/3ae409dd828ac3846240b6ba5779d18f.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/3ae409dd828ac3846240b6ba5779d18f.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/9fcdce63ed6642057249d90b1df09312.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/9fcdce63ed6642057249d90b1df09312.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all 10 boxes of the game and play this extra challenge in the room of the <strong>Elements Stone</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/44e533929a409bb1af86a864e29623d1.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/44e533929a409bb1af86a864e29623d1.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a straightforward user interface and captivating puzzles, this game promises an engaging experience that expertly balances challenge and entertainment, keeping you engaged for hours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/097faee7dbb218ba5b523f7c3212eaea.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/097faee7dbb218ba5b523f7c3212eaea.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/be74c479fa53348513a54b9cce48b485.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/be74c479fa53348513a54b9cce48b485.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each Box has its music theme, for you to play this adventure in a transcendental way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/7b204173db3e076b9e327f8a87d1fd42.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/7b204173db3e076b9e327f8a87d1fd42.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click the bulb button in the scene to get a hint that will help you solve the puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In case you got stuck on a puzzle, feel free to get in touch with the developer to get some more hints</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/db3ff9adcfcecb376959769504351842.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/db3ff9adcfcecb376959769504351842.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let your community and friends know what you're playing and how far you've gone in this escape room adventure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong> here. I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing everything myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/0a8903dd3a4b9cfd37c396ee753c8568.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/0a8903dd3a4b9cfd37c396ee753c8568.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a new series of intricate boxes filled with alluring enigmas and brain-teasing challenges that will leave you a lasting impression</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/3ae409dd828ac3846240b6ba5779d18f.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/3ae409dd828ac3846240b6ba5779d18f.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/9fcdce63ed6642057249d90b1df09312.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/9fcdce63ed6642057249d90b1df09312.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock all 10 boxes of the game and play this extra challenge in the room of the <strong>Elements Stone</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/44e533929a409bb1af86a864e29623d1.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/44e533929a409bb1af86a864e29623d1.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a straightforward user interface and captivating puzzles, this game promises an engaging experience that expertly balances challenge and entertainment, keeping you engaged for hours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/097faee7dbb218ba5b523f7c3212eaea.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/097faee7dbb218ba5b523f7c3212eaea.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/be74c479fa53348513a54b9cce48b485.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/be74c479fa53348513a54b9cce48b485.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each Box has its music theme, for you to play this adventure in a transcendental way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/7b204173db3e076b9e327f8a87d1fd42.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/7b204173db3e076b9e327f8a87d1fd42.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click the bulb button in the scene to get a hint that will help you solve the puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In case you got stuck on a puzzle, feel free to get in touch with the developer to get some more hints</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/db3ff9adcfcecb376959769504351842.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/db3ff9adcfcecb376959769504351842.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let your community and friends know what you're playing and how far you've gone in this escape room adventure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1760423381\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882350/extras_big/f221e128dbdeaebe6f4bbf6c8f11e2ae.avif?t=1760423381 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong> here. I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing everything myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p>",
